              <path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M17 17h2a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4h10z" />
            </svg>
            詳細図
