              </h3>
               <button onClick={() => setIsMailModalOpen(false)} className="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 rounded-full p-1 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                  <svg className="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                </button>
            </div>

            <div className="space-y-6">
              <div className="bg-orange-50 p-4 rounded-xl border-2 border-orange-200">
                  <p className="font-bold text-orange-800 text-sm">重要：メールを起動する前に、必ず「PDF保存」ボタンから見積書を保存してください。</p>
              </div>
              <div className="space-y-4 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                <p>この後の手順：</p>
                <ol className="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 ml-2">
                  <li>「メールソフトを起動」ボタンを押すとメール作成画面が開きます。</li>
                  <li>宛先・件名・本文は自動で入力されます。</li>
                  <li>保存した<span className="font-bold text-red-600 underline">見積書PDF、現地案内図、平面図</span>の3点を忘れずに添付してください。</li>
                </ol>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div className="mt-8 flex justify-end gap-3">
              <button onClick={() => setIsMailModalOpen(false)} className="px-6 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 text-gray-600 font-bold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">キャンセル</button>
              <button onClick={handleLaunchMail} className="px-8 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all shadow-lg active:scale-95">メールソフトを起動</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      )}

      {isModalOpen && (
        <div className="fixed inset-0 z-[400] flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-900/80 backdrop-blur-md p-4 animate-in fade-in duration-300">
          <div className="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl max-w-2xl w-full overflow-hidden animate-in slide-in-from-bottom-8 duration-500">
            <div className="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-700 to-indigo-800 p-8 text-white relative">
              <div className="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-10">
                <svg className="w-32 h-32" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-5 14H7v-2h7v2zm3-4H7v-2h10v2zm0-4H7V7h10v2z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <h1 className="text-3xl font-black mb-2 tracking-tight">内部建具・玄関収納 見積作成</h1>
              <p className="text-blue-100 text-sm opacity-90">物件名や基本仕様を入力して、正確な見積りをスピーディーに作成します。</p>
            </div>

            <div className="p-8 space-y-6">
              <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div className="space-y-2 group">
                  <label className="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest group-focus-within:text-blue-600 transition-colors">会社名 <span className="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                  <input type="text" value={initialSettings.company} onChange={(e) => setInitialSettings(p => ({ ...p, company: e.target.value }))} className="w-full border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition-all text-sm font-bold" placeholder="株式会社 ○○建設" />
                </div>
                <div className="space-y-2 group">
                  <label className="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest group-focus-within:text-blue-600 transition-colors">現場名 <span className="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                  <input type="text" value={initialSettings.siteName} onChange={(e) => setInitialSettings(p => ({ ...p, siteName: e.target.value }))} className="w-full border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition-all text-sm font-bold" placeholder="○○様邸 新築工事" />
                </div>
                <div className="space-y-2 group">
                   <label className="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest group-focus-within:text-blue-600 transition-colors">ご担当者名 <span className="text-red-500">*</span></label>
                   <input type="text" value={initialSettings.contactName} onChange={(e) => setInitialSettings(p => ({ ...p, contactName: e.target.value }))} className="w-full border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition-all text-sm font-bold" placeholder="柏木 太郎" />
                </div>
                <div className="space-y-2 group">
                   <label className="text-xs font-black text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest group-focus-within:text-blue-600 transition-colors">連絡先電話番号</label>
                   <input type="tel" value={initialSettings.phone} onChange={(e) => setInitialSettings(p => ({ ...p, phone: e.target.value }))} className="w-full border-2 border-gray-100 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 bg-gray-50 focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition-all text-sm font-bold" placeholder="090-0000-0000" />
                </div>
              </div>

              <div className="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 space-y-6">
                <p className="text-xs font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest border-b pb-2">基本デフォルト仕様</p>
                <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
                  <div className="space-y-1.5">
                    <label className="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400">標準の高さ</label>
                    <select value={initialSettings.defaultHeight} onChange={(e) => setInitialSettings(p => ({ ...p, defaultHeight: e.target.value }))} className="w-full border rounded-lg px-2 py-2 text-xs font-bold bg-white shadow-sm">
                      <option value="H2000">H2000</option>
                      <option value="H2200">H2200</option>
                      <option value="H2400">H2400</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                  <div className="space-y-1.5">
                    <label className="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400">標準の色</label>
                    <select value={initialSettings.defaultDoorColor} onChange={(e) => setInitialSettings(p => ({ ...p, defaultDoorColor: e.target.value }))} className="w-full border rounded-lg px-2 py-2 text-xs font-bold bg-white shadow-sm">
                      {COLORS.map(c => <option key={c} value={c}>{c}</option>)}
                    </select>
                  </div>
                  <div className="space-y-1.5">
                    <label className="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400">ハンドルの色</label>
                    <select value={initialSettings.defaultHandleColor} onChange={(e) => setInitialSettings(p => ({ ...p, defaultHandleColor: e.target.value }))} className="w-full border rounded-lg px-2 py-2 text-xs font-bold bg-white shadow-sm">
                      {SIMPLE_HANDLE_OPTIONS.map(c => <option key={c} value={c}>{c}</option>)}
                    </select>
                  </div>
                  <div className="space-y-1.5">
                    <label className="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400">巾木の色</label>
                    <select value={initialSettings.defaultBaseboardColor} onChange={(e) => setInitialSettings(p => ({ ...p, defaultBaseboardColor: e.target.value }))} className="w-full border rounded-lg px-2 py-2 text-xs font-bold bg-white shadow-sm">
                      {COLORS.map(c => <option key={c} value={c}>{c}</option>)}
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div className="p-8 bg-gray-50 border-t flex justify-between items-center">
               <button onClick={() => setIsDataViewerOpen(true)} className="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
                  <svg className="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924-1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" /><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
                  マスタ管理
               </button>
               <button onClick={handleStart} className="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-12 py-4 rounded-2xl font-black transition-all shadow-xl active:scale-95 flex items-center gap-3 group">
                 作成を開始する
                 <svg className="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="3" d="M13 7l5 5-5 5M6 7l5 5-5 5" /></svg>
               </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      )}

      {/* Main UI */}
      <div className="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8 space-y-6">
        {/* Header and Info section */}
        <div className="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
          <div className="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
            <div>
              <h2 className="text-2xl font-black text-gray-800 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3">
                <span className="bg-blue-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Order</span>
                物件情報
              </h2>
            </div>
            <button onClick={() => setIsModalOpen(true)} className="text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-600 text-xs font-bold transition-colors">物件情報を変更</button>
          </div>

          <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div className="space-y-4">
              <div className="flex flex-col border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                <span className="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Company</span>
                <span className="font-bold text-gray-800">{order.customerInfo.company}</span>
              </div>
              <div className="flex flex-col border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                <span className="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Project Site</span>
                <span className="font-bold text-gray-800">{order.customerInfo.siteName}</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div className="space-y-4">
               <div className="flex flex-col border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                <span className="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Address (Shipping)</span>
                <div className="flex gap-2">
                   <select value={addressPart.prefecture} onChange={(e) => handlePrefectureChange(e.target.value)} className="border rounded px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-slate-50">
                     <option value="">都道府県を選択</option>
                     {shippingFees.map(f => <option key={f.id} value={f.prefecture}>{f.prefecture}</option>)}
                   </select>
                   <input type="text" value={addressPart.detail} onChange={(e) => handleAddressDetailChange(e.target.value)} className="flex-1 border rounded px-2 py-1 text-xs bg-slate-50" placeholder="市区町村以降の住所" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div className="flex flex-col border-b border-gray-100 pb-2">
                <span className="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Contact</span>
                <span className="font-bold text-gray-800">{order.customerInfo.contactName} {order.customerInfo.phone && `(${order.customerInfo.phone})`}</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div className="bg-blue-50/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 space-y-4">
              <span className="text-[10px] font-black text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest block border-b border-blue-100 pb-2">Delivery Dates</span>
              <div className="space-y-3">
                <BusinessDatePicker value={order.customerInfo.deliveryDate1} onChange={(date) => setOrder(prev => ({ ...prev, customerInfo: { ...prev.customerInfo, deliveryDate1: date } }))} label="希望日①" colorClass="bg-blue-600" />
                <BusinessDatePicker value={order.customerInfo.deliveryDate2} onChange={(date) => setOrder(prev => ({ ...prev, customerInfo: { ...prev.customerInfo, deliveryDate2: date } }))} label="希望日②" colorClass="bg-indigo-600" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Door section */}
        <div className="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
          <div className="p-4 bg-gray-50 border-b flex justify-between items-center">
            <h3 className="font-black text-gray-700 flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg className="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10" /></svg>
              内部建具 リスト
            </h3>
            <button onClick={addDoorRow} className="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm font-black transition-all shadow-md active:scale-95 flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg className="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="3" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" /></svg>
              行を追加
            </button>
          </div>
          <div className="overflow-x-auto">
            <table className="w-full text-left border-collapse">
              <thead className="bg-slate-50 text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest border-b">
                <tr>
                  <th className="px-4 py-3 w-12 text-center">ID</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-32">部屋名</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-40">種類</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-40">デザイン</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-24">巾(mm)</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-24">高さ</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-40">枠仕様</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-24">吊元</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-40">扉色</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-40">枠色</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-40">ハンドル</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-32 text-right pr-4 bg-blue-50/30">セット価格</th>
                  <th className="px-2 py-3 w-24 text-center">操作</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                {order.doors.map((door, index) => (
                  <DoorRow
                    key={door.id}
                    index={index}
                    door={door}
                    updateDoor={updateDoor}
                    removeDoor={removeDoor}
                    initialSettings={initialSettings}
                    onShowHandleImage={() => setIsHandleModalOpen(true)}
                    siteName={order.customerInfo.siteName}
                    priceList={priceList}
                  />
                ))}
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          {order.doors.length === 0 && (
            <div className="p-12 text-center">
              <p className="text-gray-400 font-bold mb-4">建具が登録されていません</p>
              <button onClick={addDoorRow} className="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-black text-sm">最初の1行を追加する</button>
            </div>
          )}
        </div>

        {/* Entrance Storage section */}
        <EntranceStorageSection 
          storage={order.storage} 
          updateStorage={(updates) => setOrder(p => ({ ...p, storage: { ...p.storage, ...updates } }))} 
          siteName={order.customerInfo.siteName}
          storageTypes={storageTypes}
        />

        {/* Footer actions and Totals */}
        <div className="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start">
           <div className="lg:col-span-8 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 space-y-4">
              <h3 className="font-black text-gray-700 flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <svg className="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z" /></svg>
                備考・連絡事項
              </h3>
              <textarea 
                value={order.memo} 
                onChange={(e) => setOrder(p => ({ ...p, memo: e.target.value }))}
                className="w-full h-32 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm bg-slate-50 focus:bg-white focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition-all resize-none font-bold"
                placeholder="特記事項や配送に関するご要望があれば入力してください..."
              />
           </div>

           <div className="lg:col-span-4 space-y-4">
              <div className="bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6 text-white shadow-xl space-y-4 border-b-4 border-gray-900">
                 <div className="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                   <span className="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Subtotal</span>
                   <span className="text-xl font-bold font-mono">¥{totals.subtotal.toLocaleString()}</span>
                 </div>
                 <div className="flex justify-between items-baseline border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                   <span className="text-[10px] font-black text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Tax (10%)</span>
                   <span className="text-lg font-bold font-mono">¥{totals.tax.toLocaleString()}</span>
                 </div>
                 <div className="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
                    <span className="text-xs font-black text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Grand Total</span>
                    <span className="text-4xl font-black font-mono text-blue-400">¥{totals.total.toLocaleString()}</span>
                 </div>
              </div>

              <div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
                 <button onClick={handleOpenEstimate} className="bg-white border-2 border-blue-600 text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl font-black transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:scale-95 shadow-md">
                   <svg className="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
                   見積書を表示・印刷
                 </button>
                 <button onClick={handleBatchExport} className="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl font-black transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 active:scale-95 shadow-xl">
                    <svg className="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth="2" d="M17 17h2a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v4h10z" /></svg>
                    図面を一括保存・印刷
                 </button>
              </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

export default App;
